0Z","msg":"去啦緊係 係朋友都想你開心"},{"pid":"215b4e248b07a2c8f7c2e78a8a85e3fd08982d05","tid":101592,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去啦緊係 係朋友都想你開心</blockquote><br />\n但好似好撚衰"},{"pid":"3d2e46e344794f59eecc63fb02330dcc3e032cc6","tid":101592,"uid":78388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個frd知唔知你鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n唔知</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁你想唔想無左個fd？<br />\n<br />\n我朋友就係試過咁，其實都同兄弟講左又無咩表示，話睇條女點囉，但最後真係去馬之後就兄弟反目"},{"pid":"4f9d8bd02d1820d98ddfa2a09fa7fd3da810dc5b","tid":101592,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個frd知唔知你鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n唔知</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁你想唔想無左個fd？<br />\n<br />\n我朋友就係試過咁，其實都同兄弟講左又無咩表示，話睇條女點囉，但最後真係去馬之後就兄弟反目</blockquote><br />\n我就係驚呢樣野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50912236299b21f8a6ee9b44408adf0a86440140","tid":101592,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"你鐘意得都預左無fd 架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ee8ebd6c39bb65bb7fbe7a203d23241f975d5a","tid":101592,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你鐘意得都預左無fd 架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 我最驚呢樣..."},{"pid":"baf2682e5ce3affdc1d789e23504cc720d4bcf26","tid":101592,"uid":78388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個frd知唔知你鍾意佢</blockquote><br />\n唔知</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁你想唔想無左個fd？<br />\n<br />\n我朋友就係試過咁，其實都同兄弟講左又無咩表示，話睇條女點囉，但最後真係去馬之後就兄弟反目</blockquote><br />\n我就係驚呢樣野...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就視乎你自己覺得兄弟緊要定女緊要<br />\n當你決定去馬時最好有定反目既心理準備先"},{"pid":"aa5028afe1d541b90b434d94c022d6eededf85e7","tid":101592,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"收韁啦"},{"pid":"125f25c5661ac34f55bcb3c2053edcef54e5039c","tid":101592,"uid":42569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"b87ecc54ee6f7073be2a05927f6bc98b60d5f805","tid":101592,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"你識左兄弟幾耐，又識左條女幾耐?"},{"pid":"b6219157d6a8d698275a78580cdbd42e00fc2c4a","tid":101592,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你識左兄弟幾耐，又識左條女幾耐?</blockquote><br />\n識兄弟先 識多條女一個月左右啦"},{"pid":"c06ad023ec0cfa98c7e2b6e93cca43166c55c974","tid":101592,"uid":29371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"試過比好朋友搶先一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為真心當佢好朋友 嬲唔落但真係好灰 <br />\n好想證明比佢睇我無嬲 但我點諗都諗唔到話題同佢講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過咗一段時間之後 就開始覺得咁樣唔係辦法<br />\n最後叫佢比個交代我 然後就祝咗佢地幸福<br />\n依家仲係好好朋友<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得即管去做你想做嘅嘢 真係兄弟嘅話會明白你體諒你 <br />\n但你都有責任要去同個兄弟溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88519c65be3b12484e10904b15658ee8074d3351","tid":101592,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你識左兄弟幾耐，又識左條女幾耐?</blockquote><br />\n識兄弟先 識多條女一個月左右啦</blockquote><br />\n咁算啦，是但揀。又唔係莫逆之交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}